name: Dimensional Hotel
summary:
【A new work from the author of 'Deep Sea Embers'!】Beneath the daily routine, at the end of rationality, outside the world you are familiar with – there is a landscape you have never imagined.

When Yu Sheng opened the door for the first time, the world he was familiar with collapsed.

And the “truth” that goes straight to the root of the world came to him.

author: Yuan Tong
